      <title>财政委员会称马克龙的预算计划缺乏可信度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/macron-s-budget-plans-lack-credibility-fiscal-council-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政监管机构表示，法国总统马克龙计划到 2027 年将预算赤字占经济产出的比例控制在 3% 以下，这一计划缺乏可信度，需要采取前所未有的措施来抑制支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/macron-s-budget-plans-lack-credibility-fiscal-council-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:46:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
