    <item>
      <title>南非通胀放缓，不太可能触发降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/south-african-inflation-cools-to-two-month-low-in-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的通胀率在三月份跌至两个月低点，但这不太可能说服政策制定者削减借贷成本，因为由于油价上涨，预计通胀率的下降将是短暂的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/south-african-inflation-cools-to-two-month-low-in-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 和阿迪达斯 (Adidas) 盈利受关注，提振欧洲股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tech-stocks-slump-in-europe-as-asml-rattles-high-flying-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者关注最新的财报消息，欧洲股市上涨，路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 的令人欣慰的业绩刺激了奢侈品牌的上涨，这有助于抵消 ASML Holding NV 的订单低于预期后科技行业的疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tech-stocks-slump-in-europe-as-asml-rattles-high-flying-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:20:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格保持在接近纪录水平，交易者不考虑以后降息的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-traders-overlook-delayed-cuts-scenario</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管投资者权衡美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)的信息转变，黄金交易价格仍接近历史高位，鲍威尔表示美联储维持利率不变的时间可能会比原计划更长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-traders-overlook-delayed-cuts-scenario</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 00:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
